category: METRICKY PROBLEMS
category comment: 

clue: 32,000 ounces make a short one; 3,274 more make a metric one

response: a ton

clue: Metric cowboys wear 37.85-liter hats instead of these

response: a 10-gallon hat

clue: That grain of salt you're taking is just .0648 of this basic metric unit

response: a gram

clue: The measure abbreviated cu yd equals .765 of this

response: a cubic meter

clue: "THE ACRE" anagrams to this measure, 2.47 acres

response: a hectare

